{"tid":966420,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"輸到想死","createTime":"2019-01-02T19:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T07:39:53.000Z","uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fece9dc591e70605c84e6d8817bf3e37e96c4408","tid":966420,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:26:15.000Z","msg":"3:26 am"},{"pid":"38cd4d35118168e73d7b8baaf63dfb24ce519aa0","tid":966420,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:27:31.000Z","msg":"打返個飛機先再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878d69ed9b507b421854a1a8a8f44e28bf385d9a","tid":966420,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:29:38.000Z","msg":"大樹有大樹的長法；小草有小草的長法；這世上大部分的人，都是小草。你不是孤獨的。"},{"pid":"7549756e3f0763464edba94b2789326cbc59baa5","tid":966420,"uid":17358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fece9dc591e70605c84e6d8817bf3e37e96c4408","tid":966420,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:26:15.000Z","msg":"3:26 am"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:33:34.000Z","msg":"輸左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d55d178bed97b95376ac81873a67fa2cc37512f","tid":966420,"uid":72484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f234ac67d7fa6a2125f5566ff2840db410c640fd","tid":966420,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56d6e1491ffe027d98dc428706ecff19f2ea71d","tid":966420,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"真係唔掂"},{"pid":"0ea6f915c38cf7f1af5089dc23c92df1385be41a","tid":966420,"uid":64291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"5蚊入 我都想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0830c9a827810662c0a35aa80aa86f9b8bd7c88","tid":966420,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fece9dc591e70605c84e6d8817bf3e37e96c4408","tid":966420,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:26:15.000Z","msg":"3:26 am"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:39:53.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=HWnlXHF9RxL95jyyV0%2FOqG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=eb4cfaa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=HWnlXHF9RxL95jyyV0%2FOqG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=61fc1445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}